column5: The storage I had in Lefroy for 2 huts and my snowmobile is now gone. So I NEED to find storage , reasonably priced in that area. If anyone has storage or even a lead for storage PLEASE let me know as soon as possible. Thanks Dann
Well, I'm not in that area but if I can help I'd be happy to. How long do you need it for? You know where I live.
Check out some of the local farms in the area where your looking for storage Dann, I see lots around this area with outdoor spaces for rent.
Thanks Cliff, I will keep that in mind.  Thanks Lew, I'm heading up there on saturday to do just that.
Skeeter, I know a place east of Newmarket if you are interested?
Thanks cast-away. I'm interested in any where around lake simcoe. East or west side. It would be easier if it is in lefroy but right now I will look at all storage suggestions..  Thanks Dann
